    "body": "Just finished reviewing our documentation and found no mentions of either gateway.\r\nSince we use the [contracts/deployments README](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/tree/develop/packages/contracts/deployments) to publicly list all of our contract addresses, I'm going to add a note on the README so that readers know NOT to use the regular addresses of the gateway and bridge contracts and to just use the proxied implementations.\r\n\r\nI spoke about this with @snario as well and he agrees that this is the best solution to avoid people accidentally using our non-proxied implementations of the contracts. ",
